{"type": "article", "id": 59735, "title": "王一博代言彩虹糖，携程发“寻人启事”免费乘高铁 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-27T05:20:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5309, "name": "节日"}, {"id": 4618, "name": "携程"}, {"id": 738, "name": "麦当劳"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181227123754VqzIWwu43tJiEFk9.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"XDXZ\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4321207056225575?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>彩虹糖宣布王一博成为其代言人。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227121703JaAP03NG2jpXLQwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.413889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"Ltpx\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMzA5NjkxMw==&amp;mid=2650302596&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ddf326d7bbfc315e8737626a5eacc46b&amp;chksm=83ab0a3ab4dc832c3c5c1700e583c67e16bbb33e928af3ac3672321930505c54262359d41cdb&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1227AmpWSEcYC8NVaXGIzTcY&amp;key=f27627979fcd26b367f0220144b1d8daaa82ef81ced18ca8d9403f5a80d32342864dcae2233c4f44d84399d2de09908362d7d41bd4f0ef83f4b81d48546314041ed711f3ca39bd3d087c8e154e74877b&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=FiCFm4EIDDjtbt1AFD3yBYxOqQ2HJa9P%2B6lr1OXFDmBItJ9FS3Oj6V7Cj7rP6nEm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>乐高推出“舞龙套装”中国农历新年限定款，</b></a>首次在单一市场推出定制款。细节处融入了中式窗棂纹样，把蝎子和蟾蜍组成龙角寄托美好寓意。尤其是舞龙位首选择了小猪仔来和猪年呼应。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812271305105fDS9ygwbnZPhcrB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227130507HOWbpR5ydVr7uxFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227130508k6Nev4GIuASWrTZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.649038\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227130508ZS5C0I8vzmUAWhEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812271305099SRql3PN2Mhf6FE8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632813\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Ltpx\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4321629980773764?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">百事发布新年微电影“摘星者”，</a></b>由百事可乐的各品牌代言人共同出演。翟天临、刘昊然和周冬雨扮演宇航员，带着家人的担忧和寄托完成了艰难的任务，家人们自然是举起百事可乐来庆祝飞天成功。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0819bd5to2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"tAQS\" class=\"\">携程在杭黄高铁开通运营之际，<b><a href=\"https://contents.ctrip.com/activitysetupapp/mkt/index/hhgt?popup=close&amp;openapp=5&amp;pushcode=fenxiang&amp;s_guid=01D9F367-E0BB-45DD-9BF2-17A7EC6C91C0\" rel=\"nofollow\">发起“寻人启事”寻找杭黄高铁体验官</a>。</b>名叫“杭黄”或者“黄杭”的消费者在携程报名，通过携程预订高铁车票，出行之后可以等值返现。<br></p><p line=\"tAQS\">还推出“同名乘车 0 元体验”。乘车人名字中带有“杭黄高铁”四个字的任意一字就可以免费乘车。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227121832DNvSx8hftRlYiMJw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.458667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"ulpy\">麦当劳为了推广新年活动“金拱门桶”买一送一，还模仿起来了 “1818 黄金眼”，<b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4321435318584623?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">上线广告片 “1226 黄金桶”</a>。“</b>1818 黄金眼”是一档浙江本土的民生栏目，因报道了一系列奇趣的社会新闻今年迅速走红，尤其是“发际线男孩小吴”的新闻播放之后。</p><p line=\"ulpy\">依然是寻找“金”家亲人或者找名字中带有“金”字偏旁的，不过门店限量 168 张兑换券并没有强调。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0818xnvoc2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"eGT6\">雪佛兰沃兰多米奇定制版本月上市，<a href=\"https://m.chevrolet.com.cn/act/orlando/mickey/?&amp;origin=wechat-appMessage\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>在圣诞节推出“寻踪米奇”活动。</b></a>用户观看 H5 页面的广告片，回答正确问题可以获得迪士尼门票。答案都是隐藏在片中的小细节，以此来宣传新款车型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t08174kz08k\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"FFXI\">蚂蚁花呗推出买春运火车票无息分期服务，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4321442709147294?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>同时发布平面广告，通过普通用户的角度传达使用花呗，</b></a>“先回家再说”的理念。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227122343Q5LkMysBTieqPHJ7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598462\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227122344Bp3M9tlYeZkhP02a.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227122342nyXtug7i6FLASw4h.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"init\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI5NTI5NTg4OA==&amp;mid=2247489732&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f2ce9c7ecc8b2a4f9248261aa8cb1800&amp;chksm=ec54963bdb231f2d40e7bce1d848cd4b9cc4c10e9368eecc0e0ea633c5cf4df81fa9c19ef746&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1227J5j5W3PX3dst8VVeRtrI&amp;key=f27627979fcd26b3b78b390cc52d0848bc9c9f360871deabb8233c748e3a61371d864dc196e74d3196ea986cdf67c2cff903827f7ad66d38cf6fd66e06b892ca30c04481836c87e8f920ace0f1e15a54&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=FiCFm4EIDDjtbt1AFD3yBYxOqQ2HJa9P%2B6lr1OXFDmBItJ9FS3Oj6V7Cj7rP6nEm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>今日头条推出“即视”，是一款免费的快速制作广告视频工具。</b></a>它提供多种模板视频，还针对不同的行业和投放位置提供相应的解决方案。那么，万一模板用重了？</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181227122526PYx29CQqX3rN5h7l.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.919908\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"init\" class=\"\">题图来自：Unsplash<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@lu1187490788\" rel=\"nofollow\">@lu1187490788</a></p>"}